### ============================================================
### LMS API - Хэрэглэгчийн удирдлага (User Management)
### Base URL: https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
@token = 0kGkQEbg8-LXzn5DWQrR-Q
@userId = 732
@schoolId = 1
@courseId = 1
@groupId = 1
@roleId = 1


### ============================================================
### 1. НЭВТРЭХ / ГАРАХ (Authentication)
### ============================================================

### 1.1 Цахим шуудан + нууц үгээр нэвтрэх  [POST /token/email]
# @name loginEmail
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "schooladmin@must.edu.mn",
  "password": "123",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### 1.2 Утасны дугаар + нууц үгээр нэвтрэх  [POST /token/phone]
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/phone
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "99001122",
  "password": "your_password",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### 1.3 Токен шинэчлэх  [POST /token/refresh]
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

###

### 1.4 Системээс гарах (logout)  [DELETE /token]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### ============================================================
### 2. OTP - НЭГ УДААГИЙН НУУЦ ҮГ (One-Time Password)
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Цахим шуудан руу OTP илгээх  [POST /otp/email]
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

###

### 2.2 Цахим шуудан + OTP-р нэвтрэх  [POST /otp/email/login]
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "code": "123456",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### 2.3 Утас руу OTP илгээх  [POST /otp/phone]
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/phone
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "96068185"
}

###

### 2.4 Утас + OTP-р нэвтрэх  [POST /otp/phone/login]
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/phone/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "99001122",
  "code": "123456",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### ============================================================
### 3. ХЭРЭГЛЭГЧ (Users - Admin CRUD)
### ============================================================

### 3.1 Бүх хэрэглэгчийн жагсаалт авах  [GET /users]
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.2 Шинэ хэрэглэгч бүртгэх  [POST /users]
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "first_name": "Бат",
  "last_name": "Болд",
  "username": "batbold",
  "email": "bat@example.com",
  "phone": "99001122",
  "password": "Pass1234!",
  "facebook_id": ""
}

###

### 3.3 Хэрэглэгчийн мэдээлэл харах  [GET /users/:user_id]
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.4 Хэрэглэгчийн мэдээлэл засах (Админ)  [PUT /users/:user_id]
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Бат",
  "last_name": "Болд",
  "family_name": "Болд",
  "email": "bat@example.com",
  "phone": "99001122",
  "picture": "",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 3.5 Хэрэглэгч устгах (Админ)  [DELETE /users/:user_id]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 3.6 Хэрэглэгчийн бүртгэлтэй сургуулиуд  [GET /users/:user_id/schools]
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/schools
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3.7 Хэрэглэгчийн хичээлүүд  [GET /users/:user_id/courses]
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 4. ӨӨРИЙН ПРОФАЙЛ (My Profile - /users/me)
### ============================================================

### 4.1 Өөрийн мэдээлэл харах  [GET /users/me]
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4.2 Өөрийн мэдээлэл засах  [PUT /users/me]
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Бат",
  "last_name": "Болд",
  "phone": "99001122",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 4.3 Нууц үг солих  [PUT /users/me/password]
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "OldPass123!",
  "new_password": "NewPass456!",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 4.4 Профайл зураг байршуулах  [POST /users/me/picture]
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/picture
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "BASE64_ENCODED_IMAGE_DATA",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 4.5 Өөрийн бүртгэл устгах  [DELETE /users/me]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### ============================================================
### 5. ХЭРЭГЛЭГЧИЙН ЭРХҮҮД (Roles)
### ============================================================

### 5.1 Бүх эрхийн жагсаалт  [GET /roles]
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5.2 Шинэ эрх нэмэх  [POST /roles]
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Багш",
  "priority": "1",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 5.3 Нэг эрхийн мэдээлэл  [GET /roles/:role_id]
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5.4 Эрхийн нэр засах  [PUT /roles/:role_id]
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ахлах багш",
  "priority": "1",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 5.5 Эрх устгах  [DELETE /roles/:role_id]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ROLE_ID": "{{roleId}}"
}

###

### ============================================================
### 6. СУРГУУЛИЙН ХЭРЭГЛЭГЧ (School Users)
### ============================================================

### 6.1 Сургуулийн хэрэглэгчдийн жагсаалт  [GET /schools/:school_id/users]
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6.2 Хэрэглэгчийг сургуульд нэмэх  [POST /schools/:school_id/users]
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "batbold",
  "role_id": "2",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 6.3 Хэрэглэгчийг сургуулиас хасах  [DELETE /schools/:school_id/users/:user_id]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6.4 Сургуульд эрх хүсэх хүсэлт илгээх  [POST /schools/:school_id/requests]
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_id": "2",
  "description": "Би энэ сургуульд багшаар ажиллахыг хүсч байна.",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 6.5 Сургуулийн гишүүнчлэлийн хүсэлтүүд  [GET /schools/:school_id/requests]
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6.6 Гишүүнчлэлийн хүсэлт зөвшөөрөх  [POST /schools/:school_id/requests/:request_id]
# @name approveSchoolRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 6.7 Гишүүнчлэлийн хүсэлт татгалзах  [DELETE /schools/:school_id/requests/:request_id]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/requests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 6.8 Сургуулийн багш нарын жагсаалт  [GET /schools/:school_id/teachers]
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/{{schoolId}}/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================================
### 7. ХИЧЭЭЛИЙН ХЭРЭГЛЭГЧ (Course Users)
### ============================================================

### 7.1 Хичээлийн хэрэглэгчдийн жагсаалт  [GET /courses/:course_id/users]
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7.2 Хичээлд хэрэглэгч (оюутан) нэмэх  [POST /courses/:course_id/users]
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "group_id": "",
  "current_user": ""
}

###

### 7.3 Хичээлийн хэрэглэгчийн мэдээлэл  [GET /courses/:course_id/users/:user_id]
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7.4 Хэрэглэгчийн багийг өөрчлөх  [PUT /courses/:course_id/users/:user_id]
PUT {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "group_id": "{{groupId}}"
}

###

### 7.5 Хэрэглэгчийг хичээлээс хасах  [DELETE /courses/:course_id/users/:user_id]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "COURSE_ID": "{{courseId}}",
  "USER_ID": "{{userId}}"
}

###

### ============================================================
### 8. ХИЧЭЭЛИЙН БАГ (Course Groups)
### ============================================================

### 8.1 Хичээлийн багуудын жагсаалт  [GET /courses/:course_id/groups]
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8.2 Шинэ баг нэмэх  [POST /courses/:course_id/groups]
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "А бүлэг",
  "priority": "1"
}

###

### 8.3 Багийн мэдээлэл харах  [GET /groups/:group_id]
GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8.4 Багийн нэр, эрэмбэ засах  [PUT /groups/:group_id]
PUT {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course_id": "{{courseId}}",
  "name": "Б бүлэг",
  "priority": "2"
}

###

### 8.5 Баг устгах  [DELETE /groups/:group_id]
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
